<header class="jumbotron text-center bg-gray-light mb-6 border-bottom px-3">
  <div class="container-lg position-relative">
    <h1 class="alt-h1">Open Source Friday</h1>
    <p class="alt-lead text-gray mb-md-5 col-md-8 mx-auto">Once a week, every week. Take time to invest in the open source software you use and love.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container-md py-6 py-3 px-3">
  <h2 class="alt-h2 text-purple text-center">Your business depends on it</h2>

  <p class="alt-lead text-gray col-md-11 mx-auto text-center mb-6">
    Companies need open source software to run effectively.
  </p>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-12 float-left float-md-none pr-sm-4 pr-md-0 mb-md-4 clearfix">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 float-md-left mb-4 pr-md-6">
      <h3 class="alt-h3 mb-1">Attract and retain talent</h3>
      <p class="alt-text-small text-gray mb-4">
        Employees that work on open source boost their, and their employer's, reputation.
      </p>

      <h3 class="alt-h3 mb-1">Work better together</h3>
      <p class="alt-text-small text-gray mb-4">
        Open source development models are at the forefront of software collaboration. Take what you learn from open source and use it to improve quality, speed, and transparency at your organization.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
      <a href="https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/">
        <img class="card img-responsive" src="https://opensource.guide/assets/images/cards/contribute.png">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-12 float-left float-md-none pl-sm-4 pl-md-0 clearfix">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 float-md-right pl-0 pl-md-3 mb-3 mb-sm-0">
      <h3 class="alt-h3 mb-1">Improve your technology</h3>
      <p class="alt-text-small text-gray mb-4">
        Take control by contributing directly, rather than relying on others to maintain the software your business depends on.
      </p>

      <h3 class="alt-h3 mb-1">Reduce overhead</h3>
      <p class="alt-text-small text-gray mb-4">
        Regular contributions to open source save money and developer hours by reducing the custom software you need to maintain.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
      <a href="https://opensource.guide/legal/">
        <img class="card img-responsive" src="https://opensource.guide/assets/images/cards/legal.png">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>


