      <p class="text-gray mb-4">
        Encourage your managers, employees, and coworkers to spend at least two hours on one day every week to work on the open source projects your business already uses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-12 float-left float-md-none pl-sm-4 pl-md-0 clearfix">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 float-md-right pl-0 pl-md-3 mb-3 mb-sm-0">
      <h3 class="alt-h3 mb-1">Learn about how it works</h3>
      <p class="alt-text-small text-gray mb-4">
        Learn how to develop policies that let employees contribute to open source.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="d-md-table-cell v-align-middle col-md-6 text-center">
      <a href="https://opensource.guide/legal/">
        <img class="card img-responsive" src="https://opensource.guide/assets/images/cards/legal.png">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

